I have the strategy source now. The vulnerable stage is still the same public `vault.earn() -> strategy.deposit() -> add_liquidity([_y,0,0,0], 0)` path; the issue is purely that the current attacker leg burns too much value in Curve before the honest deposit happens. Next I’m probing the forked state and test harness to size a route that can skew price without making repayment impossible.
